### 🚨🚨🚨 RULE R212 - PHASE DIRECTORY ISOLATION PROTOCOL (NEW!)
**Source:** rule-library/R212-phase-directory-isolation-protocol.md  
**Criticality:** MISSION CRITICAL - Phase work must be properly isolated  
**Priority:** HIGHEST - Inject metadata into ALL phase plans

**YOU MUST ADD PHASE METADATA TO ALL PHASE PLANS:**
```bash
# 🚨 AFTER creating/receiving phase plans, inject metadata! 🚨
inject_phase_metadata() {
    local PHASE="$1"
    local PHASE_ARCH_PLAN="phase-plans/PHASE-${PHASE}-ARCHITECTURE-PLAN.md"
    local PHASE_IMPL_PLAN="phase-plans/PHASE-${PHASE}-IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN.md"
    
    # Function to inject into a plan
    inject_into_phase_plan() {
        local PLAN="$1"
        if [ ! -f "$PLAN" ]; then return 1; fi
        
        if grep -q "PHASE INFRASTRUCTURE METADATA" "$PLAN"; then
            echo "✅ Metadata already in $PLAN"
            return 0
        fi
        
        # Create metadata header
        cat > /tmp/phase_metadata.md << EOF
<!-- ⚠️ PHASE INFRASTRUCTURE METADATA (R212) ⚠️ -->
<!-- ALL AGENTS: YOU MUST ACKNOWLEDGE THIS PHASE DIRECTORY! -->
**PHASE_NUMBER**: ${PHASE}
**WORKING_DIRECTORY**: $(pwd)
**PHASE_ROOT**: $(pwd)/phase${PHASE}
**EFFORTS_ROOT**: $(pwd)/efforts/phase${PHASE}
**PHASE_PLANS_DIR**: $(pwd)/phase-plans
**INTEGRATION_BRANCH**: phase${PHASE}-integration

⚠️ **CRITICAL PHASE ISOLATION RULES** ⚠️
1. ALL phase ${PHASE} work MUST happen under: $(pwd)/phase${PHASE}/
2. ALL efforts MUST go under: $(pwd)/efforts/phase${PHASE}/
3. ALL wave work MUST go under: $(pwd)/efforts/phase${PHASE}/wave{N}/
4. Phase plans stay in: $(pwd)/phase-plans/
5. NEVER mix files between phases!

**PHASE DIRECTORY STRUCTURE**:
$(pwd)/
├── phase-plans/                          # Phase-level plans
│   ├── PHASE-${PHASE}-ARCHITECTURE-PLAN.md
│   └── PHASE-${PHASE}-IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN.md
├── phase${PHASE}/                        # Phase-specific code
└── efforts/phase${PHASE}/                # Phase efforts
    └── wave*/effort*/
<!-- END PHASE METADATA -->

EOF
        
        # Prepend to plan
        cat /tmp/phase_metadata.md "$PLAN" > /tmp/updated_plan.md
        mv /tmp/updated_plan.md "$PLAN"
        echo "✅ R212: Phase metadata injected into $PLAN"
    }
    
    # Inject into all phase plans
    inject_into_phase_plan "$PHASE_ARCH_PLAN"
    inject_into_phase_plan "$PHASE_IMPL_PLAN"
    
    # Also inject into wave plans
    for wave_plan in phase-plans/PHASE-${PHASE}-WAVE-*.md; do
        [ -f "$wave_plan" ] && inject_into_phase_plan "$wave_plan"
    done
}
```

**WORKFLOW:**
1. Architect creates phase architecture plan
2. **INJECT R212 METADATA** into architecture plan
3. Code Reviewer reads plan (acknowledges phase directory)
4. Code Reviewer creates implementation plan
5. **INJECT R212 METADATA** into implementation plan
6. All agents reading phase plans MUST acknowledge

**ACKNOWLEDGMENT REQUIRED:**
"I acknowledge R212: I MUST inject phase metadata into ALL phase plans"
