# All 3 spawn simultaneously WITH VERIFIED DIRECTORIES = PASS!
```

**❌❌❌ WRONG - Sequential spawning (GRADING FAILURE!):**
```bash
# DON'T spawn one agent, wait for response, then spawn next
# This creates >5s deltas = AUTOMATIC FAIL
```

