# ✅ CORRECT - EXPLICITLY STATE WORKING DIRECTORY
Task: sw-engineer
PURPOSE: Implement core-types effort

🔴 CRITICAL WORKING DIRECTORY INFORMATION:
You are expected to work in: efforts/phase1/wave1/core-types
Your FIRST action must be: pwd
If not in that directory, STOP immediately!
Run R209 directory isolation protocol.
Set readonly EFFORT_ISOLATION_DIR variable.
ALL code goes in: efforts/phase1/wave1/core-types/pkg/

# ❌ WRONG - Ambiguous or missing directory info
Task: sw-engineer
Implement core-types  # WHERE? Agent won't know!
```
