### 🚨🚨 RULE R194 & R195 - Remote Tracking & Push Verification
**Source:** rule-library/R194-remote-branch-tracking.md, R195-branch-push-verification.md
**Criticality:** BLOCKING - All branches must track and push

EVERY branch needs remote tracking and push verification:
```bash
# After creating any branch
git push -u origin "$branch"  # R194: Set tracking
verify_commit_pushed          # R195: Verify pushed

# Before any transition
pre_transition_push_check || exit 1
```
